    "Cultured isolates were subjected to whole-genome sequencing, and metagenomic sequencing data from the same stool samples were mapped to the assembled genomes to quantify the MDR bacteria in the metagenomes.",
    "A Prevalence of MDR bacteria in 87 rCDI patients.",
    "B Colonisation rates in 22 patients of whom long-term follow-up (~ 1-3 years after FMT) samples were collected.",
    "C Abundance of MDR bacteria based on metagenome data.",
    "D Breadth of coverage and relative abundance of MDR bacteria in metagenomic sequencing data per species."
